#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn34.55"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn34.55:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 34 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 34 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:0.2"
msgid "1. Jhānavagga "
msgstr "1. Absorption "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 55. Sātaccamūlakasappāyakārīsutta → sākaccasappāyakārīsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn34.55:0.3"
msgid "55. Sātaccamūlakasappāyakārīsutta "
msgstr "55. Persistence and What’s Conducive "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.278, sc1
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.2"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, jhāyī. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four meditators. "

msgctxt "sn34.55:1.3"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.4"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco jhāyī samādhismiṃ sātaccakārī hoti, na samādhismiṃ sappāyakārī. "
msgstr "One meditator is skilled in practicing persistently for immersion but not in doing what’s conducive to it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.5"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco jhāyī samādhismiṃ sappāyakārī hoti, na samādhismiṃ sātaccakārī. "
msgstr "One meditator is skilled in doing what’s conducive to immersion but not in practicing persistently for it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.6"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco jhāyī neva samādhismiṃ sātaccakārī hoti, na ca samādhismiṃ sappāyakārī. "
msgstr "One meditator is skilled neither in practicing persistently for immersion nor in doing what’s conducive to it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.7"
msgid "Idha pana, bhikkhave, ekacco jhāyī samādhismiṃ sātaccakārī ca hoti, samādhismiṃ sappāyakārī ca. "
msgstr "One meditator is skilled both in practicing persistently for immersion and in doing what’s conducive to it. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.8"
msgid "Tatra, bhikkhave, yvāyaṃ jhāyī samādhismiṃ sātaccakārī ca hoti samādhismiṃ sappāyakārī ca ayaṃ imesaṃ catunnaṃ jhāyīnaṃ aggo ca seṭṭho ca mokkho ca uttamo ca pavaro ca. "
msgstr "Of these, the meditator skilled both in practicing persistently for immersion and in doing what’s conducive to it is the foremost, best, leading, highest, and finest of the four. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.9"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gavā khīraṃ, khīramhā dadhi, dadhimhā navanītaṃ, navanītamhā sappi, sappimhā sappimaṇḍo tatra aggamakkhāyati; "
msgstr "From a cow comes milk, from milk comes curds, from curds come butter, from butter comes ghee, and from ghee comes cream of ghee. And the cream of ghee is said to be the best of these. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.10"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yvāyaṃ jhāyī samādhismiṃ sātaccakārī ca hoti, samādhismiṃ sappāyakārī ca ayaṃ imesaṃ catunnaṃ jhāyīnaṃ aggo ca seṭṭho ca mokkho ca uttamo ca pavaro cā”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the meditator skilled both in practicing persistently for immersion and in doing what’s conducive to it is the foremost, best, leading, highest, and finest of the four.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.11"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn34.55:1.12"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.13"
msgid "Pañcapaññāsamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.14"
msgid "(Yathā pañcapaññāsaṃ veyyākaraṇāni honti tathā vitthāretabbāni.) "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn34.55:1.15"
msgid "Khandhavaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn34.55:2.1"
msgid "Samādhi samāpatti ṭhiti ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:2.2"
msgid "Vuṭṭhānaṃ kallitārammaṇena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:2.3"
msgid "Gocarā abhinīhāro sakkacca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:2.4"
msgid "Sātacca athopi sappāyanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn34.55:2.5"
msgid "Jhānasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Absorption are complete. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.279, sc3
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.1"
msgid "Khandha rādhasaṃyuttañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: diṭṭhiokkanta → okkanti (sabbattha)
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.2"
msgid "diṭṭhiokkanta uppādā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.3"
msgid "Kilesa sāriputtā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.4"
msgid "nāgā supaṇṇa gandhabbā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.5"
msgid "Valāha vacchajhānanti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.6"
msgid "khandhavaggamhi terasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endbook">
msgctxt "sn34.55:3.7"
msgid "Khandhavaggasaṃyuttapāḷi niṭṭhitā. "
msgstr "The Book of the Aggregates is finished."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
